# Find OIS includes and library
#
# This module defines
#  OIS_INCLUDE_DIR
#  OIS_LIBRARIES, the libraries to link against to use OIS.
#  OIS_LIB_DIR, the location of the libraries
#  OIS_FOUND, If false, do not try to use OIS
